# Title: Disable Tamper Protection on Windows Defender
# Author: Austin Songer @austinsonger
# Date: 2021-08-04
# Level: medium
# Description: Detects disabling Windows Defender Tamper Protection
# MITRE Tactic: Uncategorized
# Tags: attack.defense-impairment, attack.t1685
# Reference: https://github.com/SigmaHQ/sigma/blob/master/rules/windows/registry/registry_set/registry_set_disabled_tamper_protection_on_microsoft_defender.yml

Details="DWORD (0x00000000)" TargetObject="*\\Microsoft\\Windows Defender\\Features\\TamperProtection*" NOT ((Image="*\\MsMpEng.exe" Image="C:\\ProgramData\\Microsoft\\Windows Defender\\Platform\\*") OR Image="C:\\Program Files\\Windows Defender\\MsMpEng.exe")